        proved to work fine until now :-)
        Anyway,it can happen that it really doesn't work on YOURS,because of
        a strange memory board,weird configuration etc...

                        PLEASE TELL ME ABOUT IT IN THAT CASE.
                              (See the @{"BugReport" LINK author} section)

@{fg text}@{ub}
